{
  "text": "The sample covers monthly observations of all commercial banks in the Indonesian banking industry from 2002 to 2011, which includes the recent 2008 global financial crisis (2007:Q3-2009:Q4) [CITATION_1] . Therefore, the sample covers longer period than the previous studies (e.g., [CITATION_2] and includes both crisis and normal times. Finally, I also perform instrumental variable (IV) techniques to ensure that the reverse causality problem does not bias my findings, as well as other robustness checks.",
  "correct_citation": {
